00:07:30.730 --> 00:07:34.340
I pray that you find it oh
so useful in your endeavors

00:07:34.340 --> 00:07:34.840
out there.

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:38.210
But I'd like, before I let you
go, to ask you all a question.

00:07:38.210 --> 00:07:42.300
Are any of you out there having
success getting permission

00:07:42.300 --> 00:07:45.010
from copyright owners and
monetizing your channels

00:07:45.010 --> 00:07:48.170
using methods different
from what I've shown here?

00:07:48.170 --> 00:07:50.220
If so, I would very
much appreciate it

00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:53.070
if you would write in the
comments section the steps

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:56.790
that you've used to reach
this conclusion successfully.

